events.text: WOW! good to see you after all! i was beginning to think you’d never die, [PlayerName]!
it’s kinda weird to know that you’re just a part of several different lives, huh? six other lives came before me! six! that’s insane!
and there were two after me. i wonder what’s gonna happen when we get up there?
will we all combine into one supercat? with all our skills? that’d be so cool!
my human, amiko, she was obsessed with reincarnation stuff. it was pretty weird.
if i’d known then what i know now, though, maybe i could’ve helped her out!
i wanna see if i can send her a message in the afterlife. come on, come on, let’s get moving!
